Compressing video

Fast compressing

pkg install ffmpeg 

ffmpeg -i input.mp4 -vcodec libx264 -preset ultrafast -crf 25 output.mp4
 

Just go to the selected folder using cd 

Slower but heavy compression 

ffmpeg -i input.mp4 -vcodec libx265 -crf 23 -preset superfast -acodec copy output.mp4


Merging

For videos of same quality 

ffmpeg -f concat -safe 0 -i <(for f in *.mp4; do echo "file '$PWD/$f'"; done) -c copy "fast_merge.mp4"

Keep the video in specific folder and write cd 

For videos of different quality

ffmpeg -f concat -safe 0 -i <(for f in *.mp4; do echo "file '$PWD/$f'"; done) -c:v libx264 -preset fast -crf 23 -c:a aac "unified_merged_video.mp4"
 
Keep the video in specific folder and write cd 

Trim or cut 

ffmpeg -ss 00:00:10 -i "input.mp4" -t 00:00:20 -c copy "cut_video.mp4"


Read the video name in input.mp4


Remove audio of video

ffmpeg -i "input_video.mp4" -an -c:v copy "output_muted.mp4"


